Name: V35 - DSKY LIGHT TEST
checklistText:
G&C
1. CMC GENERAL

V35 - DSKY CONDITION LIGHT TEST
				CMC - on

1			Key V37E 00E (required)
				DSKY - P00

2			Key V35E

3			Monitor the following events
			a.	All DSKY condition lts - on
			b.	ISS warning lt - on
				CMC warning lt - on
			c.	All DSKY numerical windows display "8".
				 Sign positions in R1, R2, R3 show +,
				 V, N windows flash

			Wait 5 sec

			d.	All DSKY warning lts - off
			e.	ISS lt - off
				CMC lt - off
				V, N quites Flashing
			f.	P00 will be displayed
			g.	Key RSET
				(Don't call ave. G for 15 sec)

4			V37E 00E

Steps.Text: Check lights and "8" in registers (see checklist)
